		"description": "<p>At 2nd level, you adopt a set of moves and tactics which complement your preferred combat strategies. Choose one of the following options. Each time you gain a level, you may change this choice.</p><h2>Ambusher</h2><p>When you begin your turn hidden from a creature, you gain advantage on melee attacks against it until the end of your turn.</p><h2>Carver</h2><p>When you deal sneak attack damage with a dagger, your attack deals an additional 1d6 damage. At 11th level, this additional damage becomes 2d6 damage.</p><h2>Sniper</h2><p>Once per turn, when you make an attack with a ranged weapon you can choose to add your proficiency bonus to the damage roll.</p>",
